Rotation of pages

pkg install qpdf


qpdf "input.pdf" --rotate=ANGLE:1-z -- "output.pdf"

Replace ANGLE with your desired multiple of 90:
90: Clockwise (Landscape Right)
180: Upside Down
270: Counter-clockwise (Landscape Left)
0: Original Orientation



Adding background to a PDF 

Make a PDF using an image and name it as background.pdf


qpdf "input.pdf" --underlay "background.pdf" --repeat=1 -- Final_Result.pdf



